title: Andy Warstar - 05/20/07 Nimbin, Oz
description:
Another nice performance from Andy Warstar at the Nimbin Market on his 2007 "Go Folk Yourself!" Australian Tour. 

As usual, playing

to a full, crowded market. As usual, introduced by Bo Kaan, a rebellious musician

himself (who thinks that American&#039;s and others who eat meat are the cause of

global warming... whatever)

Anyways, this is Andy relaxed and on target doing original 

songs like "Virginia&#039;s Vagina" and "Evolution Is Revolution". Good shit!

Roll a fatty, kick back, listen and enjoy ...

google andy warstar - visit www.andywarstar.com - for the warheads!
